<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- baʿ̊da qalīliⁿ rabũnā .. yā̊̉tī ại̹lay̱ mun̊taẓirīh̊
 yā̊̉kẖudẖunā liman̊ziliⁿ .. ạảʿadãhu ʿin̊da ạảbīh̊
 likaẙ yakūna maʿahu ..wamitẖ̊lahu kulũ dẖawīh̊

[V2]
 2- baʿ̊da qalīliⁿ sayajīʾu .. ạlrãbũ yasūʿu ạlạảmīn̊
 fal̊naf̊tadi ạl̊waq̊ta ại̹dẖaⁿạ .. mā dum̊nā hunā sāyỉrīn̊
 wakadẖā ḥas̊ba ạảm̊rihi .. nakūnu daẘmaⁿạ sāhirīn̊

[V3]
 3- baʿ̊da qalīliⁿ nan̊ṭaliq̊ .. min̊ gẖur̊baẗiⁿ fī dẖā ạl̊makān̊
 fal̊naḥ̊milan̊ ṣalībanā .. wāl̊ʿāra ạảẙḍaⁿạ wāl̊hawān̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ lạ yuqāsu kulũ dẖā .. bimaj̊di dẖalika ạlzãmān̊

[V4]
 4- ậmīna yā rabũ taʿāl̊ .. biḥas̊bi waʿ̊dika ạl̊yaqīn̊
 kẖudẖ̊nā ại̹laẙka fananāla .. ạlại̹r̊tẖa maʿ̊ka kabanīn̊
 wālsẖũk̊ra nuh̊dī likamāl̊ .. niʿ̊maẗi fādīnā ạlạảmīn̊</lyrics>
<title>bʿd qlyl rbnạ</title>
</song>